Introduction

Gong Jiho, also simply known as Jiho, is a South Korean singer and actress under P&Studio. She is a former member of the girl group OH MY GIRL. She debuted as a member of OH MY GIRL on April 21, 2015 with the group's self-titled mini album, "Oh My Girl". On May 9th, 2022, WM Entertainment confirmed that Jiho would be leaving the group after her exclusive contract with them has ended. On August 10, P&Studio announced that Jiho had signed on with the agency as an actress and changed her stage name to Gong Jiho.
